Philosophy</em>, Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>

<li>Allen, J., 2018, &ldquo;Megara and Dialectic&rdquo;, in
<em>Dialectic after Plato and Aristotle</em>, edited by Thomas
B&eacute;natou&iuml;l and Katerina Ierodiakonou, Cambridge: Cambridge
University Press, pp. 17&ndash;46.</li>

<li>Atherton, C., 1993, <em>The Stoics on Ambiguity</em>. Cambridge:
Cambridge University Press.</li>

<li>Bobzien, S., 1993, &ldquo;Chrysippus&rsquo; Modal Logic and Its
