Stoiker</em>, edited by K. D&ouml;ring and T. Ebert, Stuttgart: Franz
Steiner, pp. 63&ndash;84.</li>

<li>Denyer, N., 1981a, &ldquo;The Atomism of Diodorus Cronus&rdquo;,
<em>Prudentia</em>, 13: 33&ndash;45.</li>

